## M4 — Position pills shipped

`<PositionPill code={...} tone="starter" | "alternate" />` rendered:
- **Starter:** inside the player name pill, prefixed before the name. White text on `bg-black/55`, `text-[7px] font-black tracking-widest`.
- **Alternate:** to the left of each alternate name, lower-contrast (`text-white/80 bg-white/10`).
- **Other subs (overflow row below pitch):** same alternate styling.

Multi-position primary-pick: **first code in `positions[]`** (matches the user-pinned order from `PositionMultiSelect`). Empty positions → no pill.

`primaryPositionCode(player)` helper inlined in FormationPitch — pure split of the `/`-joined position string.

